{"tid":1874930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（選擇題）老母係紅底+微藍底，你仲俾唔俾口罩佢","createTime":"2020-02-11T12:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T02:17:39.000Z","uid":81657,"like":16,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"eff83ba9e39091ae634311c03876e4d2cbdb1fdd","tid":1874930,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:56:39.000Z","msg":"背景：<br />\n老母喺大陸落嚟香港幾十年，但思想依然係紅，入過共青團。認為支共救左好多支那人，所以唔會害香港人。<br />\n反送中至令佢無乜表態，會罵下警暴，但都罵人搗路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身佢有啲行動不便，亦因為8.5 個日搭唔到車覆診。<br />\n<br />\n我呢段期間都無買個全何口罩，而家出街都係用豬咀多（濾棉夠用兩個月）。<br />\n<br />\n啱啱收到電話先知佢用晒口罩問我可唔可以俾口罩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾著你會唔會俾埋僅餘（8塊）口罩俾老母？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 俾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔俾"},{"pid":"533bdb7d9bbe963c2ec90f3c5c97312b1530cb35","tid":1874930,"uid":233385,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:57:13.000Z","msg":"老母冇得唔俾"},{"pid":"feb78096a6b21fa55ce29e9213428565d6b572c0","tid":1874930,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"你洗唔洗番工？"},{"pid":"99ffb8a81772605f87227ae20fe5edb7d0621cf7","tid":1874930,"uid":93921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:58:23.000Z","msg":"唔係一齊住就咪撚畀<br />\n相信政府"},{"pid":"2f97c928244f8ac43d3c66a93208bbc3298e3c0f","tid":1874930,"uid":38563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"你同佢一齊住就一定要畀嘅<br />\n唔係我都覺得要畀"},{"pid":"6acad9a3812f4b351101ab02cad3d9a1a9c7c090","tid":1874930,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533bdb7d9bbe963c2ec90f3c5c97312b1530cb35","tid":1874930,"uid":233385,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:57:13.000Z","msg":"老母冇得唔俾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"諗起佢罵過啲學